name: LandWolf
description: What is Landwolf? Solana enthusiasts are embracing Landwolf, moving away from the frog meme trend. Since its inception, Landwolf has become a beloved icon within the crypto community, known for his laid-back and wise demeanor. Created by Matt Furie, this character finally makes its debut on the Solana chain. Join our vibrant community on Telegram and enjoy the ride with Landwolf!
